[fidelis_endpoint_alerts://<name>]
fidelis_ip_address = The IP address or hostname of the Fidelis Endpoint Web UI Server
username = Username to authenticate against Fidelis Endpoint
password = Password to authenticate against Fidelis Endpoint
ignore_cve_alerts = When enabled, alerts related to vulnerable software will be ignored.
enrich_alert_data = Enabling this will attempt an event lookup to provide greater information with the alert. This lookup can contain information that may fall under GDRP regulations.